<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="invent-vt">invent <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'vent/    美 /ɪn'vent/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>发明；创造：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Alexander Graham Bell became famous overnight by inventing the telephone.
亚历山大·格雷厄姆·贝尔因发明了电话而一夜成名。</p><footer>2011 陕西</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>编造：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We must invent an excuse for being late. 
我们得为迟到编一个理由。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>inventor  /ɪn'ventə(r)/ n [C]   </p></div>